Ascot Holdings Advances After 23% of Equity Trades in 5 Blocks

-- B y   A n u s h a   O n d a a t j i e
-- 
2011-03-18T09:19:26Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-03-18/ascot-holdings-advances-after-23-of-equity-trades-in-5-blocks.html
  Ascot Holdings Plc (ASCO)  rose as much as
25 percent to a 52-week high in Colombo trading after about 1.8
million shares, or 23 percent of its equity, changed hands in
five blocks.  To contact the reporter on this story:
